Check this code-heavy doc section for jargon:

"## Configure ILM policies

Index Lifecycle Management (ILM) lets you automate index management. Run the following in Dev Tools:

```json
PUT _ilm/policy/my_policy
{
  "policy": {
    "phases": {
      "hot": { "actions": { "rollover": { "max_size": "50gb" } } }
    }
  }
}
```

The ILM policy above configures rollover at 50 GB."
